Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天  空座市突然出现了大量的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护和露琪亚前去消灭虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在战斗中却遇到了奇怪的三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赶来的石田等人的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护击退了虚后转身去追那三人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却已经不见踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  却在意外的地方再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是搬家到了黑崎家的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  在第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三人还转学到了一护所在的班级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子怎么看都是个小学生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是大人和孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫犬龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边这位是猿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这边的这位大人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞大路  琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里搬来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么三人一起转学？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在住在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三围呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  这样的小孩也在你的守备范围吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  为什么从刚才就只有犬龙一个人在回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为琉璃千代大人是高贵的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和卑贱的人直接交谈实在有失身分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说卑贱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也说的太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别随便接近琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太随便接近她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和一护就可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我就不能说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么问题也没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  学校真是个奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿着同样的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是死神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是琉璃千代大人亲自问的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能再礼貌点回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们别靠我那么近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  奴家口渴了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个"奴家"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这么称呼自己的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这又不是在演历史剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么问题也没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还挺喜欢的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人各有异嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得很可爱呢  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿饮料来  一护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  为什么非得我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被琉璃千代大人差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就该感到光荣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就买罐果汁给她喝吧  一护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对转校生温柔点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过认真  只会自寻烦恼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干  一护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  你要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴家也刚好要回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的方向相同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以同行一段路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:05:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们回家的路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在缜密的调查后决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可没有闲暇和其他人边聊边走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请您能谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴家就是要和一护一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上我会买甜点给您吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请您忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的点心可是很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们实在有点谨慎过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬龙做饭还是那么拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好久没有像今天这么高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也可以再去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那还真是期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也能见到黑崎一护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个不错的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是个卑劣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若随意接近的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会发生无法挽回的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法挽回的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个...这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都太过操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就开始吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一个班？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 巧妙地利用了记忆置换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不造成不协调感的状态下转校进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是这样的话 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你调查了他们的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  但是却没有使用穿界门的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那个义骸怎么看都是浦原那里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们却说是商务机密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不肯告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事情的背后一定隐藏着一个巨大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚一定要潜入那房子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查清楚他们的底细
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然浦原先生说不用管他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一定没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁还没有一两个秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就暂时让他们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是太在意了  睡都睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的灵压...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  这灵压都不太寻常了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  好吵 叫人怎么睡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这灵压 和白天的你完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可以坐视不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这灵压是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬龙  这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是隐密机动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的是琉璃千代他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看来是这样没错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要追杀琉璃千代他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识一瞬间...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那把斩魄刀的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那镜面的反射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来并不只是单纯的反光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看那反光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是职业杀手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀手？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他说出追杀琉璃千代他们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  别看反光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要专心看着敌人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说胡话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不直接看着你  我也能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的斩魄刀似乎是通过反射月光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使看到那反光的敌人一瞬间意识模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  你必定会跑到我的正面来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了这点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你就不是我的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  给我说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要追杀琉璃千代他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:15:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来琉璃千代他们确有难言之隐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经击退刺客了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得太漂亮...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛突然踢我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你留下我们去战斗  而自己跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你一定要把原委告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫井上过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好把石田和茶渡也叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞大路 琉璃千代大人她是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞大路是指那个霞大路家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吗  朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四大贵族之下的上级贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初听到霞大路这个名字的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么就没有想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木...朽木?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽木是指那个朽木家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到朽木家的人竟然会在这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你们听到朽木这个姓的时候 现在才想起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对事情的解明完全没有帮助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是我的错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人是霞大路家的正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果琉璃千代大人的父母 也就是上代主人还健在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上代的当家  也就是公主的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在诞下琉璃千代大人后就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她的父亲也随后因病去世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们作为照顾她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从她出生时开始就一直养育着她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还没有继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她还实在太小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本打算等到她到了合适的年龄再继承家业的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就因为这样而发生了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时运营着霞大路家的云井尧觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此人的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不断出现家臣失踪的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎是在将与自己意见不合的家臣都肃清了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云井利用自身的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有将霞大路家占为己有的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在琉璃千代大人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也开始发生了奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云井他觉得霞大路家的正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人太碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就开始对这孩子进行暗杀行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得这样下去太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着连身边的家臣 趁着夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用霞大路家专用的穿界门 逃到了现世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以传令神机才没有检测到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您所知的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人所有的穿界门使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用传令神机是无法检测到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在尸魂界就听说过你的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那比传言更为厉害的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经见识过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追杀琉璃千代大人的刺客肯定还会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是云井暗地里利用霞大路家的权力集中起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,职业暗杀部队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托您做琉璃千代大人的保镖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵族亲属之间的内部纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被世人所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能会毁掉霞大路家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以实在无法拜托护廷十三队的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你是死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非正式的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我们是无法阻止云井的那些刺客的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抓住刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他作为罪证与云井对证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他说"这些人我都不认识" 我们就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 那些家伙只要任务失败了 就会自行了断
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是他们还拥有很恐怖的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都相当厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护  干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连朽木大人也...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在是不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我作为朽木家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是受贵族内部纷争影响很深的 不能放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃千代大人并不知道自己被人追杀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们也不想让她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不想因这种事而让她受到心理上的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你们绝对不要告诉琉璃千代大人实情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被死神代行干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死神代行的确有点本事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过一个代行而已 为什么要帮公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不抓紧进行的话 可能会夜长梦多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要得到这份家业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也实在是不易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次你要做保镖是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不知为什么就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然保护的对象是个小女孩  让我不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会尽全力帮忙的
